span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\">M&#8217;s mobile carwash &amp; more, https:\/\/gow2.com,<\/span><\/a> <span class=\"xt0psk2\"><a class=\"x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz x1sur9pj xkrqix3 xzsf02u x1s688f\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/packedandreadytravel?__cft__[0]=AZXVAHeI0rLkERisN8qsKA81NTtQjztpic1fB7ezA-VocpPrQ9XnCy4P9ze9SS-DjT0gp6-14NMJsAWpr86Zul1ygrV-FfybnhBrepsI8sZRopW-KT-yYn2lJa2XNOCFwnRYCqJC84fFu8O41Q34LSvDRUhAQvA-SZuz5ERLDR3S42Arz6wcmu8wgyhO3DOS0PI8c6PBaywQdgAhEhBguIo7&amp;__tn__=-UC%2CP-R\"><span class=\"html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\">Packed and Ready Travel, https:\/\/qrownsupport.com en <\/span><\/a><\/span><span class=\"xt0psk2\"><a class=\"x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz x1sur9pj xkrqix3 xzsf02u x1s688f\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/siengsienggiftshop?__cft__[0]=AZUGVKAN-88gtyWot9aUqS__oSWSVj3Fx6TJWDhHaBxTjOuryhAUh4-4aYiFESQqKBULsxYQoTvCZmi9rzFN39_s2saTzT29VDFfnp5azB-AkAKo2q-IJjsJePfRya5AzKJzHKxTLjYV74egegngwnFNk_3IW6XI1ktqdRL-XRaOBwr8xUpZjQozTTtm8GG4oxYuEEcL6VSOnytiMHAD930E&amp;__tn__=-UC%2CP-R\"><span class=\"html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\">Sieng Sieng <\/span><\/a><\/span><span style=\"font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', 'Bitstream Charter', Times, serif;\">konden de participanten geweldige prijzen winnen. <\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', 'Bitstream Charter', Times, serif;\"><span class=\"xt0psk2\"><a class=\"x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz x1sur9pj xkrqix3 xzsf02u x1s688f\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/profile.php?id=100064852141840&amp;__cft__[0]=AZVRpu0TwjWHNV2gTfHEF72nThRdFAkAwxdHVrF-PmdMRQ74jpLKqp1k2w7shgt1xV3CN3zZqQPiUK_Oh-zoFh2AQmjWUTqtFMxy72nhGcCj7E8l-ZdJeJ6KvdZcFpwW8zjWocT6_tyTJVs2ie08ZZ9_faOqNpkJlzlu5QjEYE1fOsEpJ5VB1T8zq3XDcyM5S9z0oBSRu8cDLumU0TBsTRwT&amp;__tn__=-UC%2CP-R\"><span class=\"html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs\">New Suriname Dream Cafe<\/span><\/a><\/span> stelt hun cafe ter beschikking en <\/span> <span style=\"font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', 'Bitstream Charter', Times, serif;\">maakt het mogelijk voor Stichting Prasoro om de BNF te houden.\u00a0<\/span> <span style=\"font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', 'Bitstream Charter', Times, serif;\">De aantrekkelijke prijzenpot en de mooie plek, maken dit evenement niet alleen mogelijk, <\/span> <span style=\"font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', 'Bitstream Charter', Times, serif;\">maar ook bijzonder aantrekkelijk voor alle deelnemers.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', 'Bitstream Charter', Times, serif;\"><em>Er waren Fantastische Prijzen en Een Goed Doel!<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', 'Bitstream Charter', Times, serif;\"><em>Hartelijk dank voor de vrijgevigheid van alle donateurs!<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p>Hieronder de aankondigingen van de afgelopen drie BNFs!<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-1009\" src=\"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Bing-1-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Bing-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Bing-1-300x300.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" \/> \u00a0<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-1008\" src=\"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Bing-2-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Bing-2-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Bing-2-300x300.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" \/> \u00a0<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-1007\" src=\"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Bing-3-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Bing-3-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/Bing-3-300x300.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" \/><\/p>\n<h4><strong>Wij wensen u te verwelkomen als donateur en\/ of deelnemer!<\/strong><\/h4>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Op 16 mei, 27 juni en 22 augustus 2024 organiseerde Stichting Prasoro hun Bingo Night Fundraising (BNF) activiteiten! Dankzij de genereuze donatie van de volgende donateurs: New Suriname Dream Cafe,\u00a0The [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-946","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-uncategorized"],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/stich